questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is behind a metal object o1, which is near and to the right of o0. Then, for another duration of at least 5 frames, o0 is to the left of o1, shaped like a cylinder, and at the top of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Material_metal(o1), Near(o1, o0), RightOf(o1, o0)), 5); Duration((LeftOf(o0, o1), Shape_cylinder(o0), Top(o0)), 5)

questions.question: An object o0 is to the right of another object o1. Then, o0 is red and is near a third object o2 while o1 is far from o2. Finally, for at least 10 frames, o0 is behind and to the right of o2, with o0 being made of rubber.
questions.dsl: RightOf(o0, o1); (Color_red(o0), Far(o1, o2), Near(o0, o2)); Duration((Behind(o0, o2), Material_rubber(o0), RightOf(o0, o2)), 10)

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is in front of another object o1, which is made of metal. Following that, o0, shaped like a cylinder, is near another object o2 and to the right of o2. Lastly, o1 is positioned behind o2, while o0 is to the right of o1.
questions.dsl: Duration((FrontOf(o0, o1), Material_metal(o1)), 15); (Near(o0, o2), RightOf(o2, o0), Shape_cylinder(o0)); (Behind(o1, o2), RightOf(o0, o1))

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is on the right side of the video frame. Following that, for a duration of at least 10 frames, the object o0 is green, to the right of another object o1, and there is an object o2 at the top of the frame. Finally, for at least 5 frames, o0 is behind o1, which is shaped like a sphere, and o0 is near o2.
questions.dsl: Duration(Right(o0), 5); Duration((Color_green(o0), RightOf(o0, o1), Top(o2)), 10); Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Near(o0, o2), Shape_sphere(o1)), 5)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is at the top of the video frame. Subsequently, for at least 10 frames, o0 is behind another object o1 and far away from a third object o2. Finally, for a duration of at least 5 frames, o2 is made of rubber, is near o1, is on the right side of the frame, and is shaped like a cube.
questions.dsl: Duration(Top(o0), 5); Duration((Behind(o0, o1), Far(o0, o2)), 10); Duration((Material_rubber(o2), Near(o1, o2), Right(o2), Shape_cube(o2)), 5)

questions.question: For at least 5 frames, an object o0 is to the right of another object o1, and a sphere o2 is at the top of the frame. Then, o0 is near o1. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o0 is purple, o2 is to the right of o1, and o0 is at the top of the frame.

questions.question: For at least 15 frames, an object o0 is behind another object o1, and o1 is to the left of o0 and further to the left of a third object o2. Both o2 is made of rubber and o1 is made of metal. Following this, for at least 10 frames, o2 is near o1, and o0 is at the top of the video frame.
questions.dsl: Duration((Behind(o0, o1), LeftOf(o1, o0), LeftOf(o1, o2), Material_metal(o1), Material_rubber(o2)), 15); Duration((Near(o2, o1), Top(o0)), 10)

questions.question: An object o0 is behind another object o1, while a third object o2 is on the right side of the video frame. Then, for at least 10 frames, o2 is made of metal and is near o0 and o1. Finally, for a duration of at least 15 frames, o2 is behind o1 and to the left of o1, and o1 is made of rubber.

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, a metal object o0 is behind another object o1, which is in front of o0. Then, for another duration of at least 10 frames, a brown object o2 is in front of o1. Finally, o1 is at the bottom of the frame and is near to o2.

questions.question: For at least 10 frames, an object o0 is at the top of the video frame. Following that, for at least 5 frames, a cube-shaped object o1 is behind another object o2, and o0 is to the left of o2. Then, for another duration of at least 5 frames, o2 is blue, o1 is near o2, and o2 is to the right of o0.
